                <h1>Where Is Panama? Discover Its Location & Significance</h1>
                <p>Panama is located in Central America, bordered by Costa Rica to the west and Colombia to the southeast. It connects the Caribbean Sea to the north and the Pacific Ocean to the south. This strategic location serves as a bridge between North and South America, making Panama an important hub for trade and travel.</p>
